-- Cross-function auto-parallelization: a `scan` factored into a helper that
-- `inline_small` won't fold (its operator has control flow). The
-- `materialize_entry_soacs` pass exposes it at the entry boundary so it
-- parallelizes into the usual multi-phase scan pipeline.
def stencil(xs: []i32) []i32 = scan(|a: i32, b: i32| if a > b then a else b, 0i32, xs)

#[compute]
entry e(xs: []i32) []i32 = stencil(xs)
